  "detailed_description": "基于经典策略魔幻对战游戏《魔卡幻想》DLC改编的Rogue LIKE游戏《魔卡奇旅》终于上线了！准备好了吗？诺艾斯城的奇异冒险旅程起航了！在这里摄政王召集了众多勇者前往调查边境的异动。作为立志想要成为伟大英雄的勇者们自然不会放过这个机会，面对千难万苦迎战诸位英雄，有的会与您结伴而行一同冒险，有的会成为你冥思苦想多次战斗才能战胜的真正对手，但唯有这样真正的胜利大结局才能打开！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>变化多端的战斗</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661950/extras/c0bb6dec213c1ea289108598c7eb8e80.poster.avif?t=1706517601\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661950/extras/c0bb6dec213c1ea289108598c7eb8e80.webm?t=1706517601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661950/extras/c0bb6dec213c1ea289108598c7eb8e80.mp4?t=1706517601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>迭代起伏的剧情</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661950/extras/260986919c98a11ea67472bb76783350.poster.avif?t=1706517601\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661950/extras/260986919c98a11ea67472bb76783350.webm?t=1706517601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661950/extras/260986919c98a11ea67472bb76783350.mp4?t=1706517601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>600多张精美卡牌</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661950/extras/5e73ad11c8ba6eef2625bd065c83068a.poster.avif?t=1706517601\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661950/extras/5e73ad11c8ba6eef2625bd065c83068a.webm?t=